><p>Si est\\u00e1s interesado en apoyar nuestra causa o deseas obtener m\\u00e1s informaci\\u00f3n sobre c\\u00f3mo puedes involucrarte, \\u00a1cont\\u00e1ctanos hoy mismo! Tu apoyo significa el mundo para nosotros y para las mascotas que ayudamos.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"justify\",\"_element_width\":\"initial\",\"_element_custom_width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":80},\"_flex_size\":\"none\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"cf26a42\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/fundacion_angel_peludos\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/03\\/contac.jpeg\",\"id\":316,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"align\":\"center\",\"hover_animation\":\"bob\",\"image_border_radius\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"100\",\"right\":\"100\",\"bottom\":\"100\",\"left\":\"100\",\"isLinked\":true},\"image_border_radius_tablet\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"\",\"right\":\"\",\"bottom\":\"\",\"left\":\"\",\"isLinked\":true},\"image_border_radius_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"\",\"right\":\"\",\"bottom\":\"\",\"left\":\"\",\"isLinked\":true},\"link_to\":\"custom\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/docs.google.com\\/forms\\/d\\/e\\/1FAIpQLScGaG4psMoYG2A9pn2cYvr_2WurUdFlPPYDiBF1BTLDFCIw7g\\/viewform\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"custom_attributes\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"b9c928a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong>Dale encima al perrito para contactarnos<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#1215AF\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
